description: I’m Rodrigo, 38 years old from Chile. I’ve been playing online poker professionally for 15+ years, I’ve also traveled the world playing live cash games. Now on top of everything I do daily for $gib I want to contribute to $gib with my own coin, which will be created this week. Project Objective: The goal is to create an alliance between Pump and Bonk, showing full transparency to the community. 70% of the fees → support & promote $gib 20% of the fees → support my own coin, to generate more volume, more fees for $gib & activity 10% of the fees → content creation, web dev & related expenses 0% for me We’ll be streaming daily on Pump playing poker, doing surprise giveaways, and more. Get ready, incredible details coming soon
